Prodorsum. Cerotegument finely granular. Cuticle dark brown laterally, median interlamellar area lighter. Rostrum triangular in dorsal view, slightly projecting anteroventrally in lateral view. Rostrum demarcated from remainder of prodorsum by transverse ridge. Rostral (
